[03:22.72]“My sense of the immediate presence of the Morlocks revived at that.  I felt that I was wasting my time in the academic examination of machinery.  I called to mind that it was already far advanced in the afternoon, and that I had still no weapon, no refuge, and no means of making a fire. 
我立即意识到莫洛克人随时可能出现。我感到钻研这些机器完全是在浪费时间，又意识到时间已是下午晚些时候。我仍然没有找到武器，没有找到藏身之处，没有找到生火的工具。

[03:41.17]“And then down in the remote blackness of the gallery I heard a peculiar（奇特的） pattering, and the same odd noises I had heard down the well. 
